title: Cant view my own or other peoples ranked stats
body: so i cant view my own or other peoples ranked stats, the **see more stats** bar is a grey color and is unclickable,has been soing it for a week now. has it been disabled for something to do with the season or is it my client?

replies.body: I have the same problem. It's been happening for at least a week. Is it an actual bug or is it just Rito who made it unclickable?
I'm assuming It has something to do with season 6 starting but not 100% positive
